<TEXT>
no college no problem if youd like to 
collect a sheepskin from the university of hard knocks where phi 
beta kappa keys are scorned and graduates include jesse helms and w 
clement stone 
we absolutely will not take a college graduate says founder 
jim comstock were very firm on that point 
comstock 79 decided to take an old adage one step further in 
1947 since then he has awarded nearly 2000 degrees he has no 
campus and holds no classes but graduates from as far away as 
canada will gather saturday night for an annual commencement 
ceremony 
applicants must be successful in a particular field donate 100 
to their prospective alma mater and buy a subscription to the 
hillbilly which offers a mix of news poetry and a satirical column 
written by comstock 
comstock editor of the weekly west virginia hillbilly newspaper 
has befriended presidents politicians and other celebrities through 
his university called uhk by its alumni 
hard knocks graduates include us sens wendell ford dky and 
jesse helms rnc former us sen barry goldwater charles o 
finley former owner of the oakland as tulsa bank millionaire lee 
braxton ventriloquist jimmy nelson arnaud de borchgrave editor of 
the washington times and chicago insurance magnate w clement stone 
theres a lot of people in the public eye who wont admit they 
didnt go to college comstock said they have to be very 
successful to admit they didnt go to college 
comstock said this years graduating class of 40 will receive 
their degrees printed in the school colors black and blue at 
aldersonbroaddus college in philippi 
comstock who lives in richwood about 45 miles east of 
charleston said he began granting degrees on a whim to bolster the 
sagging ego of his partner in the hillbilly 
my former partner bronson mcclung was kind of down one day 
because he didnt have a college degree and i did said comstock 
a marshall university graduate he said we aint paired 
correctly 
comstock found some fancy paper had university of hard 
knocks stamped across the top scribbled in some latin and 
presented the diploma to mcclung 
mcclung later left the newspaper and opened a successful bank 
i graduated with honors mcclung said the idea was 
fabulous 
hard knock graduates are a proud breed 
ive got a doctorate from uhk said john hughes president 
of the archibald candy corp which makes fannie may candy i 
suppose its because im a double dropout i dropped out of high 
school got my high school equivalent degree then dropped out of 
college 
nelson an assistant vice president for a cape coral fla bank 
and a member of the uhk class of 1984 keeps his diploma on a wall 
in his office 
im very proud of it said nelson who captured a national 
television audience in the early 1950s as the voice behind his 
ventriloquists dummies danny oday and farfel a philosophical dog 
with floppy ears 
i work with college graduates all around me said nelson who 
started in show business after high school most people think its 
a joke but it isnt its kind of tongueincheek but its nice 
to have something on the wall that means something 
</TEXT>
