million micucci said sellers usually set a reserve price a little 
bit below the low estimate 
st peter repentant was the first rembrandt painting put on 
the auction block since the artists portrait of a girl wearing a 
goldtrimmed cloak fetched 1038 million in 1986 
the st peter painting a 23by18inch oil on oak panel was put 
up for auction by an anonymous private american collector 
i was quite surprised it didnt sell said ian kennedy 
