compromise measures but balked at suspending the declaration 
yeltsin has said he expects the russian parliament to declare the 
russian federations sovereignty within the first 100 days of his 
term the russian federation is the soviet unions largest republic 
with twothirds of its territory and just over half its population 
sovereignty would mean republic authorities would have final say 
over which soviet laws are valid on russian territory and greater 
independence in general from the national government including on 
economic issues 
if russia were to resume supplying lithuania with natural gas 
oil and other raw materials it would mean the virtual end of the 
